    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this car to believe it\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this beauty since day one, and it\u2019s in pristine, mint condition inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving joy waiting for you! It runs like a total dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let it go, but I\u2019m so excited for it to find a new home with someone who will love it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
