    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 997.1 Carrera S, featuring the high-revving M97.01 3.8L boxer engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This specimen boasts a factory-fitted Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system and a mechanical limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip. Recent Blackstone oil analysis confirms optimal bearing health, and a comprehensive bore-scope inspection shows no signs of cylinder wall scoring. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation or fluid seepage. A mechanically flawless, turn-key driver for the discerning purist.",
